  "bodyHtml": "<head></head><body><div style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px;\">\n\t<div style=\"font-family:arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\" dir=\"ltr\">Dear Gregor,</span></div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Thank you for your message and for bringing your concerns to our attention regarding the handling of your personal data on ekool.eu.<br>We have reviewed the vulnerability report you submitted, along with your formal request under Articles 15, 18, and 21 of the General Data Protection Regulation (Regulation (EU) 2016/679, “GDPR”).</span></div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Our technical team has assessed the identified account enumeration behavior in the password reset, account registration, and email change forms.</span></div>\n<ul>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">CAPTCHA protection is already in place, effectively preventing automated abuse of these forms.</span></div></li>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">However, we do acknowledge that response messages and UI behavior may differ depending on whether an email is already registered. While this does not expose full user profiles or sensitive information, the fact of account existence can be considered personal data under GDPR.</span></div></li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">​​</span><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\"><br>To address this and minimize the risk of personal data disclosure, we have initiated the following steps:</span>\n</div>\n<ol>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Unifying frontend messages across all relevant forms so that no distinction is visible to the end user based on account existence.</span></div></li>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Generalizing backend responses, including HTTP status codes, headers, and response timing, to avoid indirect signals.</span></div></li>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Maintaining CAPTCHA validation to protect against large-scale enumeration attacks.</span><br><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\"><br></span>\n</div></li>\n</ol>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">​​</span><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">These updates are scheduled for implementation and testing over the coming weeks. Once completed, our system will no longer reveal whether a specific email address is registered.</span>\n</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\"><strong>Legal Basis</strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Currently, the processing in question was conducted under our <strong>legitimate interest</strong> (GDPR Art. 6(1)(f)) in providing account support functionality and preventing duplicate account creation. That said, based on your objection and our internal reassessment, we agree that this interest does not outweigh your right to data protection and privacy in this context. Therefore, we are adjusting our implementation accordingly.</span></div>\n<div>\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">​</span><br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\"><strong dir=\"ltr\">Your Rights</strong></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Your request under <strong>Article 15</strong> (right of access) has been addressed by this explanation of processing purposes and legal basis.</span></div></li>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Your request under<strong>&nbsp;Article 18</strong> (restriction of processing) is being honored through the mitigation of the enumeration risk.</span></div></li>\n<li><div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">Your objection under <strong>Article 21</strong> has been accepted; we are not continuing the processing in a manner that could reveal your account status.</span><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\"><br></span>\n</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">​​</span><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">If you have any further questions, please feel free to reply to this email.<br></span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">​</span><br>\n</div>\n<div><span dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400\">​<br></span></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\">Best regards,</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\"><b style=\"font-family: arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif, arial, sans-serif\" dir=\"ltr\">eKool team</b></div>\n<div><a href=\"https://contact.ekool.eu/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: initial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\">contact.ekool.eu</a></div>\n<div><img src=\"https://eucattachment.freshdesk.com/inline/attachment?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpZCI6MTAxMDM0Mzc0MDc4LCJkb21haW4iOiJla29vbC5mcmVzaGRlc2suY29tIiwiYWNjb3VudF9pZCI6MjQxNjU4M30.jdcaUPFRM66gyaUh0YNOs0yG-W1mYYapmteTx2Y06dw\" class=\"inline-image fr-fil fr-dii\" data-id=\"101034374078\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" height=\"38px\" data-height=\"38\" style=\"width: 111.946px\"></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<span title=\"fd_tkt_identifier\" style=\"font-size:0px; font-family:&quot;fdtktid&quot;; min-height:0px; height:0px; opacity:0; max-height:0px; line-height:0px; color:#ffffff\">26891:2416583</span>\n\n</div></body>",
